Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 以前的我又有何種的回憶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這個 我就開始坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要去尋找我的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那勾玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得布布會去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不擔心布布嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她自己決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們擔心也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 就不要再提起呂布了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別什麼都問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟去哪裡了 呂布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫…孫策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了 聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙剛才說了「你究竟去哪裡了 呂布」 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在偷聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然還是很擔心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙…蒙蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙也很擔心布布吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不去就是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說去就去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙竟然使用關節技 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥士之證
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不清楚是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老是被別人挑釁幹架 就是因為這個勾玉的緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼『鬥士』到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一頭霧水 除了自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 名字還是那些找碴兒和我幹架的傢伙告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫夏侯惇元讓 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布奉先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙真的生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還把人家趕出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布布也是 要是寫下去處就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 仲謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前公瑾哥哥有提到過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那制服 是洛陽的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於現在的呂布小姐而言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠成為尋找過去線索的 就唯有那件制服才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個 仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛陽在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛陽高校？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以問你一件事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對『孟德』這個名字有印象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟德…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛陽的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的死黨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我自己的名字都給忘了 卻還記得那傢伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是個對我很重要的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有重要的人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問問公瑾哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 蒙蒙果然很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 最近的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點過於粘人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 洛陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其君主董卓仲穎死後 漸漸失去了管制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該已經廢校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘不忍睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原來真的在這種地方上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想要確認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就奉陪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我和你都是所謂的『鬥士』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的過去中 說不定就會有我過去的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所言 對方主動上門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣的話 我也不會冒著重重危險去見蒙蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和她在一起的那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:08:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他交給夏侯淵好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都記不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的曾經在這裡上過學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方真的存在著我的回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案由我來告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『你』…被你叫得這麼生疏 還真是受挫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的習慣到敏感部位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該很瞭解我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾經是我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這種啊 真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有勾玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是鬥士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾是你女友的事情 是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是你過去的老熟人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事就問她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯惇元讓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到…許昌學院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許昌學院？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原來是那裡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我曾是你的女朋友 現在不是了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你為了某種目的而接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是看破了這點 反過來利用你罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們彼此也都曾樂在其中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你把一切都忘記了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這正好方便了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我心裡還有那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙沒有告訴過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的使命就是讓那傢伙成為真正的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯淵妙才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯惇 和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得好像你們什麼都知道似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨眼老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照夏侯淵的話去做 回到許昌來協助我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想見他吧？曹操孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要帶你…回許昌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我就說了吧 我很不爽你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 這下就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對赤手空拳的對手 使用武器太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對赤手空拳的對手 使用刀子太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 惇惇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伯符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常和你在一起戰鬥 老做傻事的伯符 你忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾玉上竟還寫著名字 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好 別叫我笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策…伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是孫策伯符嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當…當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 這麼一本正經地…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧 我忘掉了好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 有一件事情我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 你是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你叫我笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家唯獨不願意被惇惇叫笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的緣分到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又明白了一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙 仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布小姐也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好多事情想要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惇惇 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到我這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 可不可以住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把制服弄破的話 媽媽的怒吼就在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就交給我 惇惇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能一而再再而三地老是被女人救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被那傢伙帶到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了尋找過去來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽命…於我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再讓我重複了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個裝模作樣的傢伙也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想見孟德 就得協助他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在尋找的死黨孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓你們把他當作交易的籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惇惇 這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是你重要的修理工具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球的話有球場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔道的話有道場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那街頭格鬥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜謎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全玩不轉這個 因為我是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這街頭就是我們的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這片聖地搞得一團糟 你覺得可以就這樣回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥中 最重要的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯淵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要和那個裝模作樣的傢伙聯手？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說孟德就在許昌等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就要以我自己的方式去見他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我腦子裡總算是豁然開朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先這樣 在裂開的部分處塗上油灰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再用小鏟子緩緩地砌均勻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惇惇還是一如既往的蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙 布布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惇惇 你有何打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回許昌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的答案肯定在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫子有言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『朝氣銳 晝氣惰 暮氣歸』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在早上精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了中午就精力渙散 夜晚就需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來品嚐便當嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去見見媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思 伯符姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為惇惇是媽媽的男朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 搞砸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧 嬸嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 又有人在八卦我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是美發沙龍的那孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站前新開的大藥房的店長也是即可靠又出色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得…布布比以前開朗了很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在談論我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 孫策 我和你的老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…在交往？是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異常恩愛呢 媽媽的肚子已經有了惇惇的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有我的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.99,0:23:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承認 我絕對不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯惇先生 請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫子有言『負責是男人的基本精神』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 孫子有言『我…什麼都不知道』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七話 始如處女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}出自《孫子兵法》：始如處女，敵人開戶，後如脫兔，敵不及拒
